---
title: Gnocchi Primavera (v) with Courgette and Cherry Tomato
description: Juicy cherry tomatoes combine beautifully with plump little gnocchi, fried until their golden. Add a creamy pesto sauce and it becomes a symphony of summery flavour. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-pesto-gnocchi-2cb6694f-cbc45670.jpg
